\title{Peer Review in Forest}
\author{owen-lynch}
\date{2024-03-06}

\p{[[david-jaz-myers]] proposed an interesting idea, which is to have a "review" taxon that shows up in a different section than backlinks. Then people can leave reviews by writing a tree with taxon "review" that links to the tree with which they find problems.}

\p{When the review is addressed, it can be marked as such.}
